divs: sighting detailsi was living with a friend in wyoming. he took me out one day to see the beautiful landscape and mountains, etc. as we were driving down some dirt road, i saw what reminded me of a house from the flintstones, literally all stones\boulders. anyhow we stopped driving so i could take a picture. i was sitting in the passenger seat, and just took pictures out the window. (window was rolled down of course). i had my 35mm camera and my digital camera. i picked up one the cameras and snapped a picture, set it down, and took the same picture with the other camera. it wasnt till 2010 that i got my 35mm film developed... and it was a great picture of the little "hut". then i decided to finally put my memory card in a friends wii so i could look at the pics on a tv. when i came across the picture of the "hut" from the digital camera, i noticed an object in the sky. i enhanced the pic best i could to see what i could make of the object. its def not a smudge or plane or bird. id really like to have a professional examine the picture. if its not a ufo, id like to know what it actually is.
Summary: 2 pics taken, 1 with digital, 1 with 35mm. digital caught a UFO.
